---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <div class="github-main-container">
    <section class="github-header">
      <svg class="github-icon" role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="color:#24292f"><title>GitHub</title><path fill="currentColor" d="M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12 0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385.6.113.82-.258.82-.577 0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729 1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236 1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93 0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176 0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405 1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405 2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22 0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22 0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286 0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12"/></svg>
      <h1>GitHub</h1>
      <p>(Plataforma de alojamiento y colaboración para proyectos con Git)</p>
    </section>
    <section class="github-content">
      <h2>¿Qué podés encontrar acá?</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Fundamentos y conceptos de GitHub</li>
        <li>Repositorios, issues y pull requests</li>
        <li>Colaboración y flujos de trabajo</li>
        <li>Recursos y enlaces útiles</li>
      </ul>
      <blockquote class="github-quote">"GitHub potencia el desarrollo colaborativo y el open source."</blockquote>
      <a href="/blog" class="back-main-btn">Volver al inicio</a>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
.github-main-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 2.5rem 1rem 2.5rem 1rem;
  font-family: Inter, Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
}
.github-header {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
}
.github-icon {
  width: 54px;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  display: block;
  margin-left: auto;
  margin-right: auto;
  color: #24292f;
}
.github-header h1 {
  font-size: 2.1rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  letter-spacing: -1px;
  color: #24292f;
}
.github-header p {
  font-size: 1.13rem;
  color: var(--color-text, #444);
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.github-content h2 {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  color: #24292f;
}
.github-content ul {
  margin: 0 0 1.2rem 1.2rem;
  padding: 0;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.github-content li {
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}
.github-quote {
  margin: 1.5rem 0 0 0;
  padding: 1rem 1.2rem;
  background: #f5f5f5;
  border-left: 4px solid #24292f;
  border-radius: 8px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #24292f;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
}
.back-main-btn {
  display: inline-block;
  margin: 2rem auto 0 auto;
  padding: 0.7rem 2.1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #24292f 0%, #57606a 100%);
  color: #fff;
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.08rem;
  border: none;
  border-radius: 8px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px #24292f22;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background 0.18s, box-shadow 0.18s, transform 0.13s;
  cursor: pointer;
  text-align: center;
}
.back-main-btn:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #57606a 0%, #24292f 100%);
  box-shadow: 0 4px 16px #24292f44;
  transform: translateY(-2px) scale(1.04);
  color: #fff;
}
@media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
  .github-header h1 {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .github-main-container {
    padding: 1.2rem 0.3rem 1.5rem 0.3rem;
  }
}
</style>
